Package C2G8_Project.MonitorSystem

Class MainWindow

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent
javafx.scene.layout.Region
javafx.scene.layout.Pane
javafx.scene.layout.VBox
C2G8_Project.MonitorSystem.MainWindow
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class MainWindow extends javafx.scene.layout.VBox
Main window of program to show all system state data that is important. This is mostly passive but it does have a connect function. This can be connected at any time during the simulation.
Author:
Jayson Mendoza
